('', 'Oh, hello. You look like you know your way around these parts.\n\nHave you seen my sons, Jem, Jack, and Jake? They should be here somewhere.\n\nI\'m not leaving until I find my boys. I won\'t lose them again!', 207266, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 6, 1, 0, 0, 2000, 0, 38134),
