('', 'I just love creative solutions! Maybe now they\'ll think twice about stirring up trouble.', 200183, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 163486, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 38134),
('', 'These spriggans need to be stopped! I say we give them a taste of their own medicine.', 200182, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 163485, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 38134),
