('', 'Indeed. Then it is only fitting that you atone for your indiscretions... as my baron. From this day forth, you will serve as my liaison to Baroness Draka.', 196331, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 167507, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 38134),
