UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `Text`='Welcome, Maw Walker.\n\nNot everything you see is for sale. We also collect.\n\nSuch curious creatures we have found in your realm. I am enjoying expanding my collection.', `VerifiedBuild`=38134 WHERE `ID`=204537;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `Text`='Welcome, Maw Walker.\n\nThis device will allow you to access shard storage from across the dimensions that separate this world from yours. Unlike our Attendant friends over there, with their hallowed Purpose, I understand how it functions.\n\nI will not tell you how though. Consider it a trade secret. \n\nYou are however free to use it. Compliments of the Brokers.', `VerifiedBuild`=38134 WHERE `ID`=204536;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `Text`='You might be thinking right now, \"That\'s a gnome stuck inside of a strange glob of ooze. Maybe he needs help!\" Nope! Believe it or not, I chose to be in this \"thing.\" I\'m incognito, disguised, undercover... whatever you want to call it. This sack of goo is the only thing that protects me in this awful  place. Fortunately, I have made wonderful discoveries of new pets to train out here, and have a team worthy of calling champions. I\'ll battle my way to victory and gain the respect I finally deserve! The only downside is that everything I own is now sticky. Everything.', `VerifiedBuild`=38134 WHERE `ID`=204472;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `Text`='With Devos gone, Lysonia will surely take her place leading the Forsworn. I pray we find peace before their campaign starts anew.', `VerifiedBuild`=38134 WHERE `ID`=203819;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `Text1`='I see the Maw Walker is with you. I trust their choice to ally with you, and with that we can ally too.', `VerifiedBuild`=38134 WHERE `ID`=203540;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `Text`='What bring ye to Nourman\'s door?', `VerifiedBuild`=38134 WHERE `ID`=202987;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `Text`='Some soulbinds may have an advantage over a particular memory than another. One option is to have another soulbind attempt the fight.\n\nTry equipping your soulbind with equipment and charms. Equipment will grant your soulbinds an active ability, while charms are passive buffs. Both can truly turn the tide of a fight. I can tell you more about those if you would like!\n\nLastly, as you increase your renown with our covenant, your soulbinds get passively stronger. If you are struggling with a memory, perhaps give it time and focus on increasing your renown and strengthening your soulbind before trying again.', `VerifiedBuild`=38134 WHERE `ID`=202921;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `Text`='I made it out safely, but I lost some of my things during all of the confusion.  \n\nThe spriggans will destroy my tools. I just know it!\n\nI\'m afraid I cannot go back to retrieve my tools and the garden will go untended...', `Text1`='I made it out safely, but I lost some of my things during all of the confusion.  \n\nThe spriggans will destroy my tools. I just know it!\n\nI\'m afraid I cannot go back to retrieve my tools and the garden will go untended...', `VerifiedBuild`=38134 WHERE `ID`=201464;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `Text1`='Keep out of sight! The Drust are crawling all over the place, $n! Literally, crawling! They\'re up to something, something big and we have to stop it!\n\nOkay, here\'s the plan. The Drust have a bunch of sylvar defiled with those weird masks. The poor dears are completely under the Drust\'s control. There is no saving them, but we can still use them.\n\nSee this flower near me? It\'s a Dire Rose. No, don\'t touch it! Dire Rose pollen is dangerous, makes sylvar go crazy and violent till they pass out. I\'ll use some of my magic to disguise you as a common Ardenmoth. Get some of the Dire Rose pollen, sprinkle it on the defiled and cause some chaos.\n\nNo way this could possibly go wrong!\n\nWell, you ready?', `VerifiedBuild`=38134 WHERE `ID`=200928;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `Text`='Go faster, stupid thing!', `Text1`='Go faster, stupid thing!', `VerifiedBuild`=38134 WHERE `ID`=200914;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `Text`='The paragons have already assembled and await the Archon\'s arrival. It would be wise for you to listen until asked to speak.', `VerifiedBuild`=38134 WHERE `ID`=199904;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `Text1`='The Scourge have seemed restless since the sky shattered. It\'s our job to keep an eye on them. In the meantime, let\'s make sure your combat skills are sharp.', `VerifiedBuild`=38134 WHERE `ID`=199368;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `Text`='Me, a traitor? By the Maw Walker\'s presence, I can see that you\'re the real traitor. Deal with these two and return the mirror shard to me in Archivam.', `VerifiedBuild`=38134 WHERE `ID`=199135;
